org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.phd

Interface PhdBallVisitorCallback


  • public interface PhdBallVisitorCallback

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static interface  PhdBallVisitorCallback.PhdBallVisitorMemento
      PhdBallVisitorMemento is a marker interface that PhdBallFileParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its ace file in order to revisit portions of the ace file.

      • canCreateMemento

        boolean canCreateMemento()
        Is this callback capable of creating PhdBallVisitorCallback.PhdBallVisitorMementos via createMemento().
        Returns:
        true if this callback can create mementos; false otherwise.

      • createMemento

        PhdBallVisitorCallback.PhdBallVisitorMemento createMemento()
        Create a PhdBallVisitorCallback.PhdBallVisitorMemento.
        Returns:
        a PhdBallVisitorCallback.PhdBallVisitorMemento; never null.
        Throws:
        UnsupportedOperationException - if canCreateMemento() returns false.
